== 6. Nf3 ==
White proceeds with normal development. Black now has two options.

* Go into the classical variation with '''[[/6...Nbd7/]]'''.
* Go for either [[/6...h6/7. Bh4/7...Ne4|Lasker's defense]] or the [[/6...h6/7. Bh4/7...b6|Tartakower variation]] with '''[[/6...h6/]]'''.

